
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-liu-mboned-mldauth-ps-00.txt'>
    <title>"MLDv2 User Authentication Problem Statement", Ya Liu, Behcet Sarikaya, Peilin Yang</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-liu-mboned-mldauth-ps-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document defines architectural considerations and problem statement for authenticating the user before entering into a multicast group using the multicast listener discover protocol version 2 (MLDv2).  The issues regarding identifying multiple users, authenticating the channel, accounting, mobile multicast and security are identified.</description>
    <dc:date>2008-02-17T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
